## 🔧 Advanced Features Toggle (Simple Mode):
To enable/disable advanced features like MCR multi-channel routing experiments, use the `simpleModeHint` field from TypeScript Zod schema:

```typescript
// From packages/types-shared/src/lab-chapter.ts  
const highPerformanceNetChapterExample = {    
  simpleModeHint: true,      // Enable/disables MCR spraying and advanced routing challenges in UI per Phase 2 Implementation Notes  
};  

# v1.2 upgrade doc notes: Progressive depth toggle via feature flag disables MCR
```

